data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom, 2-1/2 bath Colonial in Like-new condition. Home has been completely renovated and painted. The home Features new hardwood floors throughout the first and second floors, crown molding, ceiling fans, newly renovated bathroom, finished walk-out basement with separate storage/utility area, new Lenox heater and A/C and artisan finished concrete front steps. Kitchen has new granite counter tops and blacksplash, separate breakfast area, pantry and main floor laundry with additional cabinet storage. Family room features large sliding glass doors to the deck. Master bedroom with cathedral ceilings, ceiling fan, and large walk-in closet. Newly-renovated en-suite bathroom includes soaking tub and separate large walk-in shower and a double-sink Vanity.
